latestPosts.caption: The Lune et Soleil hoops ♥️ perhaps our collection’s most underrated pair - they’re striking from afar and don’t weigh down your earlobe. They’re also perfect to add a bit of whimsy to your everyday - especially if you’re someone who believes in all things magical and otherworldly ⋆｡°✩☽*✧ ☽𖤓

Whenever we find ourselves in a creative limbo, we return to our safe place - a meditative mood board. Hours spent on Pinterest, dreaming and manifesting a world far away. Searching for the perfect visual translation of what our inner world is trying to say.

As we work on our second drop (and restock so many of your favorites), we find ourselves asking: what sets us apart? The answer was intuitively clear.
When we first began Nostoi, it was always about an internal escape. A quiet rebellion against logic and practicality. A way of remembering who we are beyond the noise. Jewellery for us became our portal to that sacred place. 

As we move deeper into the year, we’re embracing this limbo. Allowing it to slow us down - not in hesitation, but in intention. In softness. And most importantly, in lots of joy and fun❣️💌
